message "George Boole was an English mathematician who specialized in logic, especially logic rules involving  true and false.  The Boolean datatype is named in his honor.  

In code, as in life we base a lot of decisions on whether something is true or false. *\"If it is raining, then I will bring an umbrella; otherwise I will wear sunglasses.\"*  
"

goals do
